thread.title: Kate & Ken
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Kate & Ken

author: Kate & Ken
title: Kate & Ken
text:
Michael was a pleasure to deal with, worked with him from start to finish of the sale, he took ownership of selling our home and meeting our expectations. Kept us up to date with open houses and perspective buyer/s who showed an interest in our home.
Thank you Michael, we had a great result.
